schemaVersion: 1
id: music-factory-root
name: Music Factory
kind: root
version: 0.2.0
description: >
  A browser-native MIDI factory. Pick a famous public-domain song, watch the
  piano roll, listen via Web Audio synthesis, download a real .mid file. Ships
  with Ode to Joy, Für Elise, Twinkle Twinkle, Jingle Bells, Happy Birthday,
  Tetris (Korobeiniki), Canon in D, and When the Saints Go Marching In —
  plus the original Portal "Still Alive" player as a sub-app.
entry: index.md
